Package: soiltestR
Title: Soil Test Calibration in R
Version: 1.0.2
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Adrian A.", family = "Correndo",
             email = "correndo@ksu.edu", role = "cre",comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4172-289X")),
