Description: the soiltestR package is designed to assist users on the analysis of relative yield:soil test value relationships. The soiltestR package estimates critical soil test values using R following different approaches such as: i) the modified ALCC model originally described by Dyson and Conyers (2013) and modified by Correndo et al. (2017); ii) the graphical Cate & Nelson approach (Cate & Nelson, 1965), and iii) the statistical Cate & Nelson approach (Cate & Nelson, 1965).
